{"title":"Linezolid-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Linezolid-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Linezolid","guid":"aRSVEOt3LxWNx1kUFDLrPQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación:","guid":"PkEYS6wYo_4tNfjZUHZzSw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• ATB oxazolidinona","guid":"5JMUrD9zXp5JggUBBv6W1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"Espectro:","guid":"csqFLarL8zNBkPnxEqjFdQ","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• Cocos Gram (+): MSSA, MRSA, VRE (E. faecium), S. pneumoniae","guid":"rSJDZ1_m2UqatRSIuocUlw","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"foz6RNkKa9Ye8LOXUaKgRQ","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Infecciones de piel/tejido subcutáneo no complicadas (SSTI)","guid":"MnC-pBf_z45VGg1_uYZqZA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Neumonía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"• Alternativa en genotipos resistentes a otros ATB","guid":"dfhOazC-wQj83RPf4zzjBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Farmacocinética:","guid":"4fX9HzTNjMFPRlH8Q1Yi8A","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Biodisponibilidad oral excelente = Dosis VO e IV iguales","guid":"ym4YxpSmcsN92d-Y7ARxoQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• T1/2: 5 h (función renal normal), 6-8 h (ESRD)","guid":"oH14JxuvaQY6GRzR29GkbA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"• ⬇ Producción de toxinas en S. aureus o S. pyogenes (TSS) (1,2)","guid":"og2E34z1I3OIoAy3KsN1cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"0","text":"Dosis Adulto:","guid":"0IVHTXM7FgtNVdqCRHowmA","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• SSTI no complicada: 400-600 mg VO/IV c/12h","guid":"JH8_wGq5qg8MW9okoVV1uw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Otras indicaciones (neumonía): 600 mg VO/IV c/12h","guid":"7mzlKenKBc1GYKZsm4BoUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"Dosis\\NPediátrica:","guid":"rt7ZXQPGJjZrlTXpLHE4Ig","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"•  28 días (excepto SSTI\\Nno complicada):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• ≤11 años: 30 mg/kg/día (c/8h)","guid":"IwX_YlQ_m9gdPrKEHlyv6g","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"•  11 años: 600 mg c/12h","guid":"-kkYnoQt6wVKpGdVcz-ENg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• ≤28 días:","guid":"9eKOKyZhWgx58FvYGFpGog","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• <34 sem GA, PNA ≤7 días: 20 mg/kg/día (c/12h)","guid":"vvbhwqKC78ztebuYiFR-gQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• Otros: 30 mg/kg/día (c/8h)","guid":"_lndbhM-qIiQ86UJX2qpgg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"16","text":"• SSTI no complicada:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• <5 años: 30 mg/kg/día (c/8h)","guid":"SeqAfDuRORh0tQlln7AW1w","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• 5-11 años: 20 mg/kg/día (c/12h)","guid":"t8sgI5zl_T0JHXNd8CIgqQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"•  11 años: 600 mg c/12h","guid":"MxrsweZ64hA4yheGqZE9lw","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"16","text":"• Máx/día: 1200 mg","guid":"R0czLHF583REhehrMmWCAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"0","text":"Ajustes Renales:","guid":"CgQvzy5OeA_6hFmFO2iIhA","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"• ClCr o eGFR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• No necesario (según ficha técnica)","guid":"RCO_l4Mnw4UT79CM8XQ9Ww","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• Posible: 300 mg c/12h si eGFR <60 (3,4)","guid":"oe9IzEbWEOsRsbQK4ZOCRg","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"• HD, CAPD, CRRT:","guid":"24AE5q6nTg0sVwiMysyX9Q","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• No ajuste necesario","guid":"mciyFvgVM7HArWmPFRwJUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"28","text":"• SLED: No datos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Ajustes Hepáticos:","guid":"bUlrEWEmyPwNxF5IdgONtQ","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• No recomendado. Posible sobreexposición en cirrosis → ajuste según MIC del patógeno (5)","guid":"JWJu0Nj5tdPUM4ovRZZsiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"Otros Ajustes:","guid":"L8JRrJpXgjyV6DOn2zxh_w","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Obesidad: Datos recientes sugieren que la dosis estándar puede ser insuficiente","guid":"LYZIUS0y8JqoYZZahtnx9g","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• ECMO: ↑ dosis puede ser necesaria","guid":"6EbOfWOhIkL-NJTruQk0VQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"0","text":"Efectos Adversos:","guid":"mcDjfDHE3tWGyJWts6wlVw","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Corto plazo: Rash, náuseas (3%), vómitos (1%), diarrea (4%),\\Ncolitis por C. difficile, ↑ LFTs (1,3%)","guid":"KTst6g1Bxi-YQph21CI6gQ","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"• Largo plazo (>2 semanas): Mielosupresión reversible (trombocitopenia,\\Nanemia, neutropenia), acidosis láctica, neuropatías periférica/óptica (6)","guid":"p29ZBaQ68cP-B8nNpHN0Tg","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• ↗︎ Riesgo en ESRD","guid":"TShMo9kJ2tRPvy0IS0IzZg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Asociación con toxicidad mitocondrial en 16S RNA (7,8)","guid":"yiLljfK4gclIueogB3TpBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"• Inhibidor de MAO → Riesgo de síndrome serotoninérgico con ISRS (9)","guid":"h-ufiLD042mazvxY-6fY5w","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"40","text":"• Efectos raros: Lengua negra vellosa, nefritis intersticial aguda, tinción dental reversible (10,11)","guid":"X2drptwDthO6D_jruZxc6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"Embarazo/Lactancia:","guid":"0la40D_bDZhhTvYudlSrWw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Riesgo FDA: Categoría 1 (sin evidencia de toxicidad en humanos,\\Nletalidad embrio-fetal en ratones a 6.5x exposición humana)","guid":"VRpbKETowCUDnMvtzrDCOw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Lactancia: Probablemente seguro c